    feat: complete auto-delete system with email warnings
    
    - Add monthly account cleanup worker (1st of month at 2:00 AM)
    - Implement 5-month and 11-month email warnings before deletion
    - Use system-wide email configuration from admin settings
    - Add professional HTML email templates with clear warnings
    - Include proper cascade deletion for all related data
    - Add comprehensive logging and error handling
    - Update documentation with worker system details
    - Test email functionality with MailHog integration
    
    Features:
    - 5 months inactive: Send warning email (30 days before deletion)
    - 6 months inactive: Delete account and all data
    - 11 months suspended: Send warning email (30 days before deletion)
    - 12 months suspended: Delete account and all data
    - Monthly scheduling: Automatic cleanup on 1st of each month
    - System email config: Uses admin panel email settings
    - Professional emails: HTML templates with clear warnings and instructions

